#wrapper.d-md-flex

  = render 'support/sidebar'

  #page-content-wrapper
    .container-fluid
      %h1.mt-4 How to sign up as a Seller:
      %p
      Signing up with Afillio is free but only registered users can sell on Afillio. When you sign up, your account will automatically be a Seller account. To become a Vendor, please follow these instructions.
      %p
      Almost anyone can find a product they are passionate about to sell on Afillio. Browse our various categories, see where your skills fit in and decide how you want to sell. 
      %p
      Customers who purchase from you pay Afillio in advance. When the purchase is successfully completed, you will receive the listed commission from the total order value. For example, if you sell a product for $10 with a listed commission of $5, you will receive $5 for a completed purchase.
